---
<section class="premise" id="about" aria-labelledby="premise-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="premise-inner">

      <div class="premise-text">
        <h2 class="premise-heading" id="premise-heading">
          Not an environmental argument. A common-sense upgrade.
        </h2>
        <p class="premise-body">
          The American lawn is a monoculture that demands more pesticides than industrial
          agriculture and more emotional energy than it returns. We have been taught to see
          it as a status symbol, but it is actually a maintenance debt we have been paying
          for decades.
        </p>
        <p class="premise-body">
          ROOTED follows the movement to flip the script. By restoring native biodiversity
          to our own backyards, we are not just saving the bees &mdash; we are bringing back
          the vibrant, living landscape that belongs in our home ground.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="premise-image">
        <!-- REPLACE: film still or meadow footage frame, landscape orientation, 4:3 ratio -->
        <div
          class="img-placeholder-film-still"
          role="img"
          aria-label="[REPLACE: film still or meadow footage frame, landscape orientation]"
          data-replace="true"
        ></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .premise {
    padding: var(--space-24) 0;
  }

  .premise-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .premise-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .premise-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 65ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .premise-body:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .img-placeholder-film-still {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    background: linear-gradient(155deg, #1e3320 0%, #2e5028 50%, #3f6435 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    /* REPLACE WITH: film still or meadow footage frame */
    /* Photo spec: 4:3, min 1200px wide, AVIF+WebP stack, compress <200KB */
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .premise-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }

    .premise-image {
      order: -1;
    }
  }
</style>
